<!-- ============ HEADER (shared shell) ============ -->

<!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
<section class="hero">
  <Svg19 class="botan hero-botan-tl" aria-hidden="true" />
  <Svg20 class="botan hero-botan-br" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <p class="eyebrow">Zuo Yue Zi Meal Plan</p>
    <h1>Easy Meal</h1>
    <p class="cn-title">輕享月子餐</p>
    <p class="hero-sub">Recovery That Fits Your Life</p>
    <p class="lede">You've earned a gentle month. <em>Every-other-day delivery</em> is one full day of food — with room left for the days your family cooks.</p>
    <p class="hero-price"><span class="from">15 full days of meals · 15 deliveries within 30 days</span>{usd(products.local_easy_15d.price)}</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#pricing" class="btn btn-primary">See what's included</a>
      <a href="#taste" class="btn btn-ghost">Try a taste first</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- HERO BANNER IMAGE — replace with a wide, warm hero shot of a full Easy Meal day (~1600×640) -->
  <div class="hero-banner reveal">
    <div class="img-slot">
      <!-- <img src="images/easy-hero.jpg" alt="A full day of Easy Meal food — soups, entrées, rice and vegetables"> -->
      <span class="slot-icon">❀</span>
      <span class="slot-label">Hero Image</span>
      <span class="slot-hint">Wide, warm shot of one full Easy Meal day · ~1600 × 640</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ OPENING ============ -->
<section class="opening">
  <div class="narrow reveal">
    <p>Someone at home has already offered to help — your mother, your mother-in-law, your husband. What makes you pause probably isn't <em>whether</em> someone will cook. It's whether they'll wear themselves out doing it.</p>
    <p>A full postpartum day is a lot to make from scratch. It's easy for one big pot of soup to stretch across three days — or for a willing helper who doesn't know Zuo Yue Zi to reach for the wrong ingredients, blurring the stages that are meant to cleanse first and nourish later. All heart, not always the right food for the moment.</p>
    <p class="pull">Every-other-day delivery is one full day of food — with room left for the days your family cooks.</p>
    <p>Delivering every other day lets your family still prepare some of your meals, without standing over the stove all month — while every other day, you get a complete day of proper, stage-by-stage recovery food. They don't burn out. You still heal well.</p>
    <p>And if you're not sure Chinese postpartum food will suit your taste, the rhythm helps there too: our meals on delivery days, your own familiar food in between. No all-or-nothing.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="floral-divider reveal">
  <span class="line"></span>
  <Svg21 aria-hidden="true" />
  <span class="line r"></span>
</div>

<!-- ============ DAILY ============ -->
<section class="daily" id="daily">
  <Svg22 class="botan daily-botan" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">What Arrives Every Other Day</p>
      <h2>A full day of healing, every time</h2>
      <p>Each of your fifteen deliveries brings:</p>
    </div>
    <div class="daily-grid reveal">
      <div class="daily-cell">
        <!-- IMAGE — a warming soup / broth dish (~600×400) -->
        <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish Photo</span><span class="slot-hint">A warming soup or broth · ~600 × 400</span></div>
        <div class="cell-body">
          <div class="num"><span>一</span></div>
          <h3>A complete day, not a lighter one</h3>
          <p>Breakfast, lunch, and dinner in full — the same eleven items as the Classic plan, balanced the traditional way to restore strength, energy, and gut health.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="daily-cell">
        <!-- IMAGE — sesame oil chicken or a braise (~600×400) -->
        <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish Photo</span><span class="slot-hint">Sesame oil chicken or a braise · ~600 × 400</span></div>
        <div class="cell-body">
          <div class="num"><span>二</span></div>
          <h3>Warm, cooked-from-scratch dishes</h3>
          <p>Nothing pre-packaged, nothing shortcut. Every dish is built on hours of slow simmering and warming ingredients that support postpartum circulation and gentle recovery.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="daily-cell">
        <!-- IMAGE — a neatly plated daily meal set (~600×400) -->
        <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish Photo</span><span class="slot-hint">A packed day's meal set, ready for delivery · ~600 × 400</span></div>
        <div class="cell-body">
          <div class="num"><span>三</span></div>
          <h3>A rhythm with room in it</h3>
          <p>Fifteen deliveries across your thirty days, arriving every other day — so the food is there when you need it, and the table is free when your family wants to cook.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ GALLERY ============ -->
<section class="gallery" id="gallery">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">On the Table</p>
      <h2>A look at the food</h2>
      <p>Real dishes from an Easy Meal delivery.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-grid reveal">
      <!-- IMAGE — hero dish, tall (~800×880) -->
      <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Feature Dish</span><span class="slot-hint">Tall hero dish · ~800 × 880</span></div>
      <!-- IMAGE — square (~520×440) -->
      <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish</span><span class="slot-hint">~520 × 440</span></div>
      <!-- IMAGE — square (~520×440) -->
      <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish</span><span class="slot-hint">~520 × 440</span></div>
      <!-- IMAGE — square (~520×440) -->
      <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish</span><span class="slot-hint">~520 × 440</span></div>
      <!-- IMAGE — square (~520×440) -->
      <div class="img-slot"><span class="slot-icon">❀</span><span class="slot-label">Dish</span><span class="slot-hint">~520 × 440</span></div>
    </div>
    <p class="gallery-note">Menus rotate across your fifteen deliveries to follow the recovery sequence.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="floral-divider reveal">
  <span class="line"></span>
  <Svg21 aria-hidden="true" />
  <span class="line r"></span>
</div>

<!-- ============ PERSONA ============ -->
<section class="persona">
  <Svg23 class="botan persona-botan" aria-hidden="true" />
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="persona-grid reveal">
      <div class="persona-left">
        <p class="eyebrow">Perfect For You If…</p>
        <h2>You have help at home. We fill the gaps.</h2>
        <p>The Easy Meal is for the mom who wants to supplement her meals, not replace all of them. Full days of recovery food, at a pace that leaves room for everyone else.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="persona-right">
        <p>Maybe your mother or mother-in-law flew in and has already claimed the kitchen — and a daily delivery would only mean good food going cold in the fridge. Or you like cooking, and you want a plan that makes space for it.</p>
        <p>Maybe you're watching the budget, and you'd rather do fifteen real days of Zuo Yue Zi than stretch for thirty. Or maybe this whole tradition is new to you, and you'd like to step in gently before committing your entire month — <em>curious, not certain, and that's a perfectly good place to start</em>.</p>
        <p>Whichever one sounds like you, the food is the same food. Only the rhythm is yours to choose.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ QUOTE ============ -->
<section class="quote-band">
